{
  "name": "Driving Intent",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "type": "String",
      "label": "Description",
      "value": "<p>You bestow a target with clarity and resolve, providing a +\t2 SL to tests to resist Charm and Intimidation. When cast upon yourself, you may instead choose to receive a +2 SL bonus to Charm Tests, provided you only speak the truth. The College of Light frowns upon this latter application as a form of glamour.</p><p>\n\n <b>Lore:</b> You may inflict one @Condition[Blinded] Condition on those targeted by Lore of Light spells, unless they possess the Arcane Magic (Light) Talent. If a target has the @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.items.v3uzEthcq0JRar0J]{Daemonic} or @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.items.PFTD9gDvRWW9uh5g]{Undead} Creature Traits, spells also inflict an additional hit with Damage equal to your Intelligence Bonus that ignores Toughness Bonus and Armor Points.<p>"
    },
